{
  "id": "adv_main_02_12_02",
  "title": "東京編2章32話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tears-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい。私達じゃ、勝てません、でした……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry. We… couldn't win…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 9.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（無理もない。月のテンペストにとって初の大敗北だ）\n（……これまで敗北がなかった訳じゃない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(It can't be helped. It's Moon Tempest's first major defeat.)\n(…It's not like they've never lost before.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.0866666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（だが、今回は絶対に負けられないステージだった）\n（なのに負けた。どれほど辛くて、苦しいだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But this was a stage they absolutely couldn't lose on.)\n(And yet they lost. How painful and agonizing it must be.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4966666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 28.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "私、負けるのがこんなに辛いんだって\n今日、初めて知りました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I learned today‚ for the first time‚\nhow painful it is to lose.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（気持ちは分かる、なんて軽々しくは言えない）\n（分かるのは、ステージに立った者だけなんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I can't lightly say I understand how you feel.)\n(Only those who have stood on stage can understand.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 48.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "私達がこれまで戦って、勝ってきた相手も\nみんな、こんなに苦しい気持ちだったんでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did all the opponents we fought and won against\nfeel this painful too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……懸けるものが大きければ大きいほど\n負けた時の苦しさも、大きくなると思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…The more you have at stake‚\nthe more painful it is when you lose.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 66.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "そう、なんですね\nそんな風に考えたこと……今まで、ありませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…\nI… never thought about it that way before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 79.9
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 82.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "……教えて下さい\nこの気持ちは、どうしたら楽になれるんですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Please tell me.\nHow can I make this feeling go away?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 87.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "これまで私達が勝ってきた相手に\nなんて言えば、いいんでしょう……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should I say to the opponents\nwe've defeated…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 98.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（気付けば渚達、他の四人も）\n（琴乃と俺のやりとりをじっと見つめていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I noticed that Nagisa and the other four are also)\n(staring intently at Kotono and me.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 105.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Manager-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 107.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "お願いします、{user}さん……\n私達に、言葉をかけてくれませんか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ Manager-san…\nWon't you say something to us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（俺が慰めても、きっと解決にはならない）\n（この苦しみは、自分達で克服しなければならないんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Even if I comfort them‚ it won't solve anything.)\n(They have to overcome this pain on their own.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 123.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "……様子を見に来てみれば、なんなの？\nみんな揃って酷い顔ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What's this? Coming to check on us?\nYou all have awful faces.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 123.9333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "莉央……さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio… -san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 132.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "僕もいるんだけどね\nやぁみんな、お疲れ様",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm here too.\nHey everyone‚ good work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 266.6666666000026,
          "startTime": 132.9333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 137.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん……葵さん……\nごめんなさい。私達、勝てませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san… Aoi-san…\nI'm sorry. We… couldn't win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 148.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "負けるのが、こんなに辛いなんて、知りませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't know losing was this painful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 155.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "バカね。知らなかったの？\n負けて悔しいのなんて、当たり前でしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You idiot. You didn't know?\nOf course it's frustrating to lose!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "私達が、NEXT VENUSグランプリで\n貴方達に負けて、どんな思いをしたと思ってるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you think it felt like when we\nlost to you at the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 169.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "負けられないステージだったし、全力を出し切った\nそれでも負けた。何度も思い返しては、苦しんだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was a stage we couldn't lose on‚ and we gave it our all.\nBut we still lost. I agonized over it‚ replaying it in my mind countless times.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 178.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめんなさい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 182.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
